<HR size="1" color="#dedfdf">
<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">
Yeah all of us know that EQ is a whole lot of fun to play...... usually. I mean when u first got the game it was like WOW this is so much fun. but then as the game goes on and especially when u hit the 30 lvls it just becomes a total camp/lvl fest. I mean, think about it, what actually GOOD items are there to get at lower lvls or even at the middle lvls? not very many. so what do u do? u lvl of course. Which brings us to another problem. Hell lvls and penalty lvls. need i say more. sure i can understand hell lvls kind of. i mean, verant just wants tons of cash even though they already rake in something like 2.6 million a month but thats besides the point. hell lvls slow u down and make lvling take longer. verants reasoning behind this is that if u get to the top to fast u wont play anymore. well in my mind its quite the opposite. if i was high lvl id be playing my booty off questing and getting items and such. but as it stands. it takes WAY to much to time to lvl and even if u do, the risks, especially higher up are TREMENDOUS. i have a mage who is lvl 35. he has been so for three months. now most of you are thinking wow what a loser. no not really, just plainly, i cannot solo.yes most of u think mages are great soloers and im here to tell you, no they are not. if u want to solo, make a necro. again verant says that well if everyone could solo then there would be no purpose for groups which is what they want. now, i can understand grouping but FORCED grouping is beyond me. i mean, i HATE putting my xp bar in the hands of some other group member who might not even know what hes doing. i have died more times in lvl 35 and in 36 causing me to go back to 35 because the cleric was too busy full healing his 100hp that he lost or the wizzy that would not nuke more then once because he was afraid of aggro. or the tank that freaked out and ran because he lost 2 bubs of hp. and being a mage of course my pet aggros half the world on me and comes back saying "Hey master, look what i've found" now some of you are saying, well why dont you just quit then if u are so angry? well i am going to quit. UO sucks and EQ is getting worse and worse but there is nothing else out there right now. Personally, im just using EQ as a pastime for the better stuff in a few months as are many of my friends. I dont see how EQ is going to compare to games like shadowbane and NWN when they come out. considering that the rules in EQ are getting more strict by the day to the point where if u train a crypt mummy on a lvl 52 u can get banned for it. Maybe verant will learn from some of the stuff they are doing or maybe they will just reply with their usual "it works as intended" crap. either way, ive already canceled my account and they're not getting my $10 a month anymore. i just hope they dont push back the release dates on NWN and shadowbane.
</FONT>
<HR size="1" color="#dedfdf">
