Very true...<P>Something to look forward too though.  At lvl 45+, the players generally know how to play their characters. There are some exceptions, either those that got power-leveled, or those that bought their chars, but generally the 45+ players are good group members.  And it's a lot safer to get exp in a group then it is soloing.<P>So - just bear with it a few more lvls.  35-40 sucked, and I pretty much went all over, although the entrance to KK was okay.  After 40, go to the DL and you can group until 48, then solo if you want until 50 or 51.  Then go to KC.  Higher risks still, but the groups are MUCH better.<P>AbMagFab baFgaMbA<BR>54th High Elf Elementalist
