Future, I will throw my 2cp in here.  It doesn't matter what class you play.  You WILL get get out of the game exactly what you put into it.  If you are playing this game because you like RP type games, if you like interfacing with other people, or even if you want to solo forever (or some combo of) you will enjoy your class.  You can ask hundreds of pwople what they like about different classes and you will get hundreds of answers.<P>You will either see the glass half full, or you will see it half empty.  It all depends on you.<P>P.S. If you are just starting a character though...read through and try to find one that seems to be like you, or like something you want to be.  There is more to this game than levels and numbers if you want to look.   <IMG SRC="http://forums.castersrealm.com/eq/biggrin.gif">
