lemme fill in some folks on a wizards supposed mana regen spell.  it costs 330 mana.  it regens 1 mana per tick.  it is also a damage shield, so chances are slimm it will stay around for 330 ticks to even pay for itself.  <BR>our other mana regen is the spell harvest, which i love, but it takes a spell slot away from us.
</FONT>
